---

## Architecture Summary

This project demonstrates more than EDI parsing.

It shows how an operational integration platform can combine:

- File ingestion
- Cloud orchestration
- SQL-based transformation
- WMS staging
- API design
- Web monitoring
- Authentication
- Controlled AI assistance
- Data lake analytics
- Deployment automation

The architecture is intentionally small enough for a portfolio project while still reflecting common enterprise integration patterns.
